{"tid":1176383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重慶GDP增速回落 官方歸咎薄熙來治理不力","createTime":"2019-05-29T07:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T09:15:06.000Z","uid":144372,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2aca38ef4b33a54619d2988bd72854e9ef1202dc","tid":1176383,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T07:48:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/6184415/article-%E9%87%8D%E6%85%B6gdp%E5%A2%9E%E9%80%9F%E5%9B%9E%E8%90%BD-%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E5%8A%8D%E6%8C%87%E8%96%84%E3%80%81%E7%8E%8B%E3%80%81%E5%AD%AB%E9%81%BA%E6%AF%92/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F6184415%2Farticle-%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2585%25B6gdp%25E5%25A2%259E%25E9%2580%259F%25E5%259B%259E%25E8%2590%25BD-%25E5%25AA%2592%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%258A%258D%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2596%2584%25E3%2580%2581%25E7%258E%258B%25E3%2580%2581%25E5%25AD%25AB%25E9%2581%25BA%25E6%25AF%2592%2F&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LhPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=7ebc4e14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/6184415/article-%E9%87%8D%E6%85%B6gdp%E5%A2%9E%E9%80%9F%E5%9B%9E%E8%90%BD-%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E5%8A%8D%E6%8C%87%E8%96%84%E3%80%81%E7%8E%8B%E3%80%81%E5%AD%AB%E9%81%BA%E6%AF%92/</a><br />\n<br />\n今年兩會期間，「重慶GDP增速回落」再次成為外界關注重慶的焦點之一。「中國新聞周刊」文章稱，多位受訪者表示，<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重慶GDP增速回落，「也有薄王(薄熙來、王立軍)主政重慶時打壓民營經濟</span></span></ins></strong>，孫政才主政時不重視民營經濟的歷史原因」。<br />\n<br />\n據該周刊報導，「重慶GDP增速回落」再次成為外界關注重慶的焦點之一。3月6日，全國人大代表、重慶市委書記陳敏爾回應稱，一個區域的經濟發展不可能一直是高速增長。高增長已經難以為繼，出路就是高質量發展，這勢在必行。<br />\n<br />\n官方數據顯示，重慶市自2016年以來經濟增速放緩，地區生產總值增速回落到個位數，2018年全市地區生產總值2兆363.19億人民幣，同比增長6.0％，低於8.5％的預期，也是近年來首次低於全中國平均增速。<br />\n<br />\n陳敏爾稱，重慶經濟增長回落到個位數，是個開放的問題，是看得見、想得透的一個問題，其原因包含周期性變化、結構性變化、市場變化等多方面，需客觀看待。<br />\n<br />\n陳敏爾以重慶兩大支柱產業電子信息和汽車製造舉例稱，市場發生了一些變化，需求出現了變化，供給也會相應地發生變化。他強調，在一時的增速回落面前，需要堅定信心，保持定力與清醒，力推創新。<br />\n<br />\n報導並稱，有多位受訪者表示，重慶GDP增速回落，既與該市主要支柱產業經濟下滑、主動「擠水分」等因素有關，也有薄王主政重慶時打壓民營經濟，孫政才主政時不重視民營經濟的歷史原因。"},{"pid":"6149775330ad89a62f6ec38239690fc4579e8d93","tid":1176383,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T07:49:07.000Z","msg":"回帶咩而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04178a25a70d14d580b30404fc89803f8bb48f47","tid":1176383,"uid":254183,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T07:59:10.000Z","msg":"拿死人鞭屍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff992e0fee6a182ab3e8d5d74f0516ed7695d8e","tid":1176383,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6149775330ad89a62f6ec38239690fc4579e8d93","tid":1176383,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T07:49:07.000Z","msg":"回帶咩而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T08:04:35.000Z","msg":"2019年03月18日 06:02"},{"pid":"978422e316d4a3d74a261a59e5737ffc70454778","tid":1176383,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T08:10:33.000Z","msg":"遲下香港經濟差係因為滿清割讓香港畀英國"},{"pid":"28c86aaf330f7a20c256936020fbcbbbfe7ee666","tid":1176383,"uid":185045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T08:12:32.000Z","msg":"佢俾人趕左落台幾年，到2019年有咩衰都仲關佢事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71ef83555ff51bf681e542ae78edf0b3809d46f","tid":1176383,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28c86aaf330f7a20c256936020fbcbbbfe7ee666","tid":1176383,"uid":185045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T08:12:32.000Z","msg":"佢俾人趕左落台幾年，到2019年有咩衰都仲關佢事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T08:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6388a6cf559f32b48e7d9de33738297c04f3f32e","tid":1176383,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28c86aaf330f7